==Chinese==
===Phrase===
[[Simplified Chinese]]: 一朵鲜花插在牛粪上
[[Traditional Chinese]]: 一朵鮮花插在牛糞上
[[Pinyin]]: yī dŭo xīan hūa chā zài níu fèn shàng
# {{idiom}} A beautiful or talented woman who marries an ugly or untalented husband.
===Etymology===
Literally: A bouquet of flowers stuck into a pile of cow manure.
